=============================================================
USER API
==============================================================
METHOD (GET)
---------------------------------------------------------------
* api/v1/users/:id  //GET USER BY ID USER (AUTH REQUIRED)
	-COLUMN REQUIRED : id /(SENT PARAMS)
---------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------
METHOD (POST)
* api/v1/users/register //REGISTER USERS 
	-COLUMN:first_name,
            last_name,
            email,
            password,
            avatar_url,
            gender(1/0),
            aggrement(1/0),
            bod /(SENT BODY)
---------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------
METHOD (PUT)
* api/v1/users/update/:id  //UPDATE USERS BY ID (AUTH REQUIRED)
	-COLUMN:first_name,
            last_name,
            email,
            password,
            avatar_url,
            gender(1/0),
            aggrement(1/0),
            bod,
            instagram_url,
            facebook_url,
            avatar_url,
            gender,
            company,
            phone,
            about
---------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------
METHOD (PUT)
* api/v1/users/change-password/:id //CHANGE PASSWORD BY ID USER (AUTH REQUIRED)
    -COLUMN:password_old,
            password_new
---------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------
METHOD (PUT)
* api/v1/users/change-avatar/:id //CHANGE AVATAR BY ID USER (AUTH REQUIRED)
    -COLUMN:avatar_url
---------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------
METHOD (PUT)
* api/v1/users/change-cover/:id  //CHANGE COVER BY ID USER (AUTH REQUIRED)
    -COLUMN:cover_url
---------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------
METHOD (PUT)
* api/v1/users/deactived-user/:id //DEACTIVED USER BY ID (AUTH REQUIRED)
---------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------
METHOD (DELETE)
* api/v1/users/delete-user/:id //DELETE USER BY ID (AUTH REQUIRED)
---------------------------------------------------------------




CAFEMATES = untuk show user yang nongkrong
